verbose_text: Clinical reports have also provided another excellent example of this allelic hierarchy, where two CDH23 alleles with truncation variants led to USH type 1D, while one CDH23 truncated allele and one CDH23 missense allele led to DFNB 12, a nonsyndromic type of recessively inherited SNHL [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: CDH23 truncated allele and one CDH23 missense allele led to DFNB 12
